I have the very same problem. 
@RobinKa did you solve this?
OK, I found the cause, I missed the `--use_dml` switch! 
so the actual command shouwld be : 
```python
.\build.bat --cmake_generator "Visual Studio 16 2019" --config Release --build_wheel --use_dml --parallel 
```
You can now download it via pip from https://pypi.org/project/onnxruntime-directml/
